==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nombril
<hw>Nom"bril</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>nombril</ets>, for OF. <ets>lombril</ets>, i. e.,
<ets>ombril</ets>, with the article, a dim. fr. L. <ets>umbilicus</ets>
the navel. See <er>Navel</er>.]</ety> <fld>(Her.)</fld> <def>A point
halfway between the fess point and the middle base point of an
escutcheon; -- called also <altname>navel point</altname>. See
<er>Escutcheon</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Nome</ent>⟦br⟧
